divs: Sighting DetailsIn 1992 i was a senior in high school and studying for test on the night the incident happened. It was about 1:00 in the morning and started to feel a little tired laid down and could not go to sleep. When i got up i heard a low humming noise coming from outside my first impression was i left my guitar amp on stand by and forgot about it but that was not the case. When the noise became more drowning i went to my window and opened my shades and i felt this sense of calming fear,and intrigue all at once. I saw 3 triangle,diamond shaped objects getting larger or getting closer i could not tell but the strange thing i could not see any thing else except the objects and this emence golden light. I wanted to run outside to see what this was or scream for my parents, i could not do anything. The next thing i knew the alarm clock going off and my mom coming in the room telling me it was time for school. It felt like a half an hour went by not seven hours.

Summary: I was going to bed one night when i heard low humming noise outside where there was 3 diamond ,triangle shaped objects hovering in the sky it was about 1:00 am and i passed out and woke up at 7:00 am thinking only a few minutes had passed.
